c: 35
v: 13
t: "Yenjisinjia eshilo mushitere ne yenjisia eshitere mushilo, ne yakhola eliuba nende omwesi okhumuwulila, biosi bichendanga okhula ebise biarebwaho. Oyo niye Nyasaye Omulesi wenyu owuli nende obwami . Ne balia abamulaamanga abalali Ye, babula shiosi shiosi kata shinga olububi lweyitende"